projectGridLines.title: AI Assist Auto Labelling
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Annotate driving images and improve object tracking performance for AI-

assisted auto-labelling project.

Skill sets: Python, OOPS, PyTorch, Deep learning, GenAI

Traits expectation: Good debugging skills, ability to cover edge cases.

Expected learning: Object detection, object tracking, Transformers.

Specific courses required for project execution:Data structure & algorithms, Artificial

Intelligence, Software engineering, Distributed computing (optional).

projectGridLines.title: AI/ML Prediction of right material curve based on Test data for Suspension Components
projectGridLines.description:
Description: Predict the right Mat parameters based on Force vs Displacement(Test data) curves

for Suspension components to avoid multiple FEA-Simulation Iterations.

Skill sets: Python, ML Techniques, Coding, Basic AI skills, FEA Methods

Traits expectation: Logical Thinking, Problem Solving, Fundamentals & Understanding of

Mechanical Components and Finite Element Methods

Expected learning: Understand/ Define right ML techniques & Evaluation methods

Specific courses required for project execution: Automobile Engineering, FEA , ML & AI Basics,
